{"tid":1148474,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返套鬼片戲名","createTime":"2019-05-10T13:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T16:24:28.000Z","uid":1814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3cc8094687ac62634bf794b4d9faedfd6b20cd6","tid":1148474,"uid":1814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:10:49.000Z","msg":"好似係上年年尾係new monday fd page 睇到預告嘅  唔記得幾時上映 <br />\n<br />\n預告內容大概係講隻鬼可以偽裝成人 <br />\n<br />\n預告裡面有兩姐妹 <br />\n<br />\n其中一幕係家姐夜晚去阿妹間房搵佢 不過就唔見阿妹係房 之後發現原來呀妹係衣櫃裡面 <br />\n<br />\n阿妹出返黎 就返上床 不過就係床上跌咗d嘢係地下 叫家姐幫手執返 <br />\n<br />\n咁阿姐就彎地身執 見到有個同呀妹一樣樣個人趴係床下底裡面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 床下底呀妹就細聲對家姐講：噓 祂還在上邊嗎？<br />\n最後家姐望返床上 先發覺 床上個個唔係阿妹黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打知道套戲名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff874a05aef10ee0ca217b2dd022af3bd00ffa3","tid":1148474,"uid":1814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693ce7c8c2b2b301ced3ab10b2fecb0220daf6e4","tid":1148474,"uid":236794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"短片就有"},{"pid":"2603066a7b6a0f01476a8d8b71fb2e9aec167d5f","tid":1148474,"uid":1814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"693ce7c8c2b2b301ced3ab10b2fecb0220daf6e4","tid":1148474,"uid":236794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"短片就有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"有無link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b4fc654476062bd9febf52df52f2ca629931f9","tid":1148474,"uid":1814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:25:11.000